      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.css"
      integrity="sha512-phGxLIsvHFArdI7IyLjv14dchvbVkEDaH95efvAae/y2exeWBQCQDpNFbOTdV1p4/pIa/XtbuDCnfhDEIXhvGQ=="
      crossorigin="anonymous"
      referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/aos@next/dist/aos.css" />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.12.0-2/css/all.min.css"
      integrity="sha256-46r060N2LrChLLb5zowXQ72/iKKNiw/lAmygmHExk/o="
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@100;900&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@500&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/main.css" />
    <link rel="icon" href="../assets/synapse brain.png" />
    <script src="../js/script.js" defer></script>
    <title>Synapse | Home</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <a href="/" class="imgcontainer">
        <div>
          <img
            class="synapse-logo"
            src="../assets/synapse-logo.svg"
            draggable="false"
          />
        </div>
      </a>
      <nav>
        <ul class="mainmenu">
          <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="/forum">Forum</a></li>
          <li><a href="/resources">Resources</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
      <% if( name ){ %>
      <form action="/logout?_method=DELETE" method="POST">
        <button class="reg-btn" type="submit">Log Out</button>
      </form>
      <% } else{ %>
      <a class="log-btn" href="/login"
        ><button class="reg-btn">Login</button></a
      >
      <% } %>

      <button class="light-check">
        <img class="light-img" src="../assets/brightness.png" />
      </button>
      <% if (name) { %>
      <div class="name-user" style="user-select: none"><%= name %></div>
      <% } %>
      <button class="hamburger">
        <div class="bar"></div>
      </button>
    </header>

    <nav class="mobile-nav">
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/forum">Forum</a></li>
        <li><a href="/resources">Resources</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
        <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>

    <section class="section-one">
      <div class="section-text">
        <div
          class="title"
          data-aos="fade-left"
          data-aos-duration="1000"
          data-aos-once="true"
        >
          Limitless Possibilities.
        </div>
        <div
          class="small-span"
          data-aos="fade-right"
          data-aos-duration="1000"
          data-aos-once="true"
        >
          Organizing communities and providing resources to integrate artificial
          intelligence into society.
        </div>
        <% if (!name) { %>
        <a href="/register"><button class="reg-btn">Join Us</button></a>
        <% } %>
        <a href="/forum"><button class="reg-btn">Explore</button></a>
        <a href="/resources"><button class="reg-btn">Learn</button></a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="white-section">
      <div class="white-section-text">
        <div
          class="title"
          data-aos="fade-right"
          data-aos-duration="1000"
          data-aos-once="true"
        >
          Why Artificial Intelligence.
        </div>
        <div class="span-container">
          <p
            class="small-span"
            data-aos="fade-right"
            data-aos-duration="1000"
            data-aos-once="true"
          >
            Artificial intelligence (AI) makes it possible for machines to learn
            from experience, adjust to new inputs and perform human-like tasks.
            Most AI examples that you hear about today – from chess-playing
            computers to self-driving cars – rely heavily on deep learning and
            natural language processing. Using these technologies, computers can
            be trained to accomplish specific tasks by processing large amounts
            of data and recognizing patterns in the data.
          </p>
          <a
            href="resources.ejs"
            data-aos="fade-right"
            data-aos-duration="1000"
            data-aos-once="true"
            ><button class="learn-btn">Learn More</button></a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
      <img
        class="white-section-img"
        src="../assets/aiimage.png"
        data-aos="fade-left"
        data-aos-duration="1000"
        data-aos-once="true"
      />
    </section>

    <section class="section-two">
      <div
        class="card"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-duration="1000"
        data-aos-once="true"
      >
        <img src="../assets/brain.svg" alt="" />
        <div class="container">
          <h4>Artificial Narrow Intelligence (ANI)</h4>
          <p>
            Narrow AI is specifically goal-oriented, that is used to designed to
            perform singular tasks such as face recognition, driving car, speech
            recognition/voice assistants, or browsing the Internet.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="card"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-duration="1000"
        data-aos-once="true"
      >
        <img src="../assets/Cloud_1.svg" alt="" />
        <div class="container">
          <h4>Artificial General Intelligence (AGI)</h4>
          <p>
            AGI is a concept of a machine that possesses general intelligence
            that can mimic human behavior or intelligence and is capable of
            learning and applying this knowledge to solve any problem.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="card"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-duration="1000"
        data-aos-once="true"
      >
        <img src="../assets/Laptop_1.svg" alt="" />
        <div class="container">
          <h4>Artificial Super Intelligence (ASI)</h4>
          <p>
            Apart from understanding human behavior, AI where machines surpass
            the capability of human intelligence and become self-aware is the
            area that is called Artificial SuperIntelligence.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-three">
      <img
        class="section-three-img"
        src="../assets/section-three.png"
        data-aos="fade-right"
        data-aos-duration="1000"
        data-aos-once="true"
      />
      <div
        class="section-text"
        data-aos="fade-left"
        data-aos-duration="1000"
        data-aos-once="true"
      >
        <div class="title">Why is Artificial Intelligence Important?</div>
        <div class="text">
          Today, the amount of data that is generated, by both humans and
          machines, far outpaces humans’ ability to absorb, interpret, and make
          complex decisions based on that data. Artificial intelligence forms
          the basis for all computer learning and is the future of all complex
          decision making. Computers are extremely efficient at calculating
          these combinations and permutations to arrive at the best decision.
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-five">
      <div class="section5-text">
        <div
          class="title"
          data-aos="fade-right"
          data-aos-duration="1000"
          data-aos-once="true"
        >
          Uses of Artificial Intelligence In Real Life.
        </div>
        <div
          class="small-span"
          data-aos="fade-right"
          data-aos-duration="1000"
          data-aos-once="true"
        >
          Every industry has a high demand for AI capabilities – including
          systems that can be used for automation, learning, legal assistance,
          risk notification and research. Specific uses of AI in industry
          include:
        </div>
        <div class="subtitle">
          <h2
            data-aos="fade-right"
            data-aos-duration="2000"
            data-aos-once="true"
          >
            Medical Sciences
          </h2>
          <div
            class="small-span"
            data-aos="fade-right"
            data-aos-duration="1000"
            data-aos-once="true"
          >
            AI applications can provide personalized medicine and X-ray
            readings. Personal health care assistants can act as life coaches,
            reminding you to take your pills, exercise or eat healthier.
          </div>
          <img
            class="uses-img"
            src="../assets/microscope.png"
            data-aos="fade-left"
            data-aos-duration="1000"
            data-aos-once="true"
          />
          <h2
            data-aos="fade-right"
            data-aos-duration="2000"
            data-aos-once="true"
          >
            Banking and Financial Institutes
          </h2>
          <div
            class="small-span"
            data-aos="fade-right"
            data-aos-duration="1000"
            data-aos-once="true"
          >
            Artificial Intelligence enhances the speed, precision and
            effectiveness of human efforts. In financial institutions, AI
            techniques can be used to identify which transactions are likely to
            be fraudulent, adopt fast and accurate credit scoring, as well as
            automate manually intense data management tasks.
          </div>
          <img
            class="uses-img"
            src="../assets/bank.png"
            data-aos="fade-left"
            data-aos-duration="1000"
            data-aos-once="true"
          />
          <h2
            data-aos="fade-right"
            data-aos-duration="2000"
            data-aos-once="true"
          >
            Gaming and Entertainment
          </h2>
          <div
            class="small-span"
            data-aos="fade-right"
            data-aos-duration="1000"
            data-aos-once="true"
          >
            From virtual reality games to modern games today, this is one
            industry where artificial intelligence has taken the biggest leap.
            The bots are always present to play with you, and therefore you are
            not required to have a second person to play.
          </div>
          <img
            class="uses-img"
            src="../assets/computer-game.png"
            data-aos="fade-left"
            data-aos-duration="1000"
            data-aos-once="true"
          />
          <h2
            data-aos="fade-right"
            data-aos-duration="1000"
            data-aos-once="true"
          >
            Air Transport
          </h2>
          <div
            class="small-span"
            data-aos="fade-right"
            data-aos-duration="1000"
            data-aos-once="true"
          >
            One of the major systematic transport in the world is air transport
            and there became an urgent need to optimize the way they are
            operated. Here came the involvement of artificial intelligence where
            the machine is involved in planning the routes, along with flight
            landing and take-off charts.
          </div>
          <img
            class="uses-img"
            src="../assets/airplane.png"
            data-aos="fade-left"
            data-aos-duration="1000"
            data-aos-once="true"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
      <div class="left-footer">
        <div class="footer-title">Limitless Possibilities.</div>
